  <brief_title>Stavanger University Hospital Inflammatory Bowel Disease Trial</brief_title>
  <acronym>SUSI</acronym>
  <official_title>Management of Inflammatory Bowel Disease in the Stavanger Area - a Prospective Evaluation of Standardized Treatment Regimens on Disease Outcome With Focus on Mucosal Healing and Associations to Fatigue</official_title>
