  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims at studying the outcomes of a protocol-based handling of newly diagnosed
      Inflammatory bowel disease ( IBD ) patients within a defined uptake area in Norway. It is a
      descriptive study and no hypothesis is predefined.

      Cytokine studies, QoL and fatigue assessment will be included for hypothesis-generating
      purposes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
